4ï¸âƒ£ Blowfish âš ï¸ Old but flexible :-

1.Key size 32-448 bits, block size 64 bits, slower than AES.

=======================================================================================================================
5ï¸âƒ£ ChaCha20 ğŸš€ Modern & Fast :-

1.It is stream cipher not a block.
2.Very fast in Mobile Devices.
3.It is used in TLS, HTTP/3.
4.It is supports from Java 11+.
Notes:- If u want to using this enc & dec we need to add Bouncing Castle jar to our library
        version below 1.70.

