=======================================================================================================================
Steps to create AES Encryption & Decryption :-
=======================================================================================================================
1.Generate a Secret Key using KeyGenerator with key size & return as SecretKey.(javax.crypto.*)
      KeyGenerator keyGen = KeyGenerator.getInstance("AES");
      keyGen.init(256);
      SecretKey key = keyGen.generateKey();

2.Do Encryption using doFinal() in that pass the plainText in Bytes through Cipher.
      Cipher cipher = Cipher.getInstance(ALGORITHM);
      cipher.init(Cipher.ENCRYPT_MODE, key);
      byte[] encryptedBytes = cipher.doFinal(plainText.getBytes());
      return Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(encryptedBytes);

3.Do Decryption using doFinal() in that pass the Bytes data & return String doFinal().
      Cipher cipher = Cipher.getInstance(ALGORITHM);
      cipher.init(Cipher.DECRYPT_MODE, key);
      byte[] decryptedBytes = Base64.getDecoder().decode(cipherText);
      return new String(cipher.doFinal(decryptedBytes));

=======================================================================================================================
Steps to create AES Encryption & Decryption :-
=======================================================================================================================
1.Generate a Secret Key using KeyGenerator with key size & return as SecretKey.(javax.crypto.*)
      KeyGenerator keyGen = KeyGenerator.getInstance("AES");
      keyGen.init(256);
      SecretKey key = keyGen.generateKey();

2.Do Encryption using doFinal() in that pass the plainText in Bytes through Cipher.
      Cipher cipher = Cipher.getInstance(ALGORITHM);
      cipher.init(Cipher.ENCRYPT_MODE, key);
      byte[] encryptedBytes = cipher.doFinal(plainText.getBytes());
      return Base64.getEncoder().encodeToString(encryptedBytes);

3.Do Decryption using doFinal() in that pass the Bytes data & return String doFinal().
      Cipher cipher = Cipher.getInstance(ALGORITHM);
      cipher.init(Cipher.DECRYPT_MODE, key);
      byte[] decryptedBytes = Base64.getDecoder().decode(cipherText);
      return new String(cipher.doFinal(decryptedBytes));

